C++: no "using" or "using namespace"; always generate absolute names
Java: no "import";  always generate absolute names

Assemblies: "import" statement; no cmd. line paramter for IDL files

Java: generate thread-safe local adapters; the component is the sync. object

Java and C++: general concept for interface-proxies

Java and C++: general concept for singletons

C++: local adapter: try/catch to ensure the "throw" declaration;
     no "throw" declaration in impl. interface
     
